OL,3,CKarren Brady to leave West Ham after
OL,4,C16 years as vice-chair
OL,6,FKarren Brady is stepping down as vice-
OL,7,Fchair of West Ham, the club have
OL,8,Fannounced.
OL,10,FThe 57-year-old Baroness, best known
OL,11,Fto the public for her role as an
OL,12,Fadviser to Lord Sugar on the BBC show
OL,13,F'The Apprentice', has been in the role
OL,14,Ffor over 16 years.
OL,16,FHer departure comes with the Hammers
OL,17,Ftwo points and one place above the
OL,18,FPremier League relegation zone with
OL,19,Ffive matches to play.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
