OL,3,CKarren Brady to leave West Ham after
OL,4,C16 years as vice-chair
OL,6,FBrady took up her role with West Ham
OL,7,Fafter David Gold and David Sullivan
OL,8,Fbought the club.
OL,10,FShe previously worked as managing
OL,11,Fdirector at Birmingham after Sullivan
OL,12,Fpurchased that club.
OL,14,F"It has been a privilege to work
OL,15,Falongside the board, management,
OL,16,Fplayers, staff and supporters at West
OL,17,FHam United.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
