OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776767959
OL,3,CKarren Brady to leave West Ham after
OL,4,C16 years as vice-chair
OL,6,F"Together we have achieved remarkable
OL,7,Fmilestones, but the highlight for me
OL,8,Fwill always be lifting the UEFA Europa
OL,9,FConference League trophy ` a moment
OL,10,Fthat will stay with me forever. I am
OL,11,Fdeeply grateful for the relationships,
OL,12,Fchallenges and opportunities that have
OL,13,Fshaped my time at the club."
OL,15,FDuring Brady's tenure the club
OL,16,Fcompleted their move from Upton Park
OL,17,Fto the London Stadium, which was built
OL,18,Fas the flagship venue for the 2012
OL,19,FOlympic Games.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@\O]
