OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776767959
OL,3,CKarren Brady to leave West Ham after
OL,4,C16 years as vice-chair
OL,6,FBrady added: "While this chapter
OL,7,Fcloses, my passion for football and
OL,8,Fcommitment to supporting the next
OL,9,Fgeneration of leaders remains
OL,10,Fundiminished. I wish West Ham United
OL,11,Fevery success for the future and look
OL,12,Fforward to following their continued
OL,13,Fachievements with pride."
OL,15,FSullivan, the club's chair, described
OL,16,FBrady as an "exceptional leader" and
OL,17,Fadded: "We wish her every success in
OL,18,Fher future endeavours and thank her
OL,19,Ffor her outstanding contribution over
OL,20,Fthe past 16 years."
